headline: Dell Technologies: Buy The Dip Before The Next Refresh Cycle
summary: Dell aims for 3-4% annual top-line growth and 8% EPS growth, with plans to return over 80% of adjusted free cash flow to shareholders. Learn more on DELL stock here.
